metadata.name: Navegando
metadata.description: Navegando it's a song that I create in collaboration with my friend Manuel Bulla (Bulla Beatz) when I was in Medellin Colombia some yesterdays ago. The collectors of this music nft will participate in a raffle to win 5% of streaming royalties;One holder will be randomly selected to be added to the split sheet for collect revenue$ during one year.  The giveaway starts when the sale ends.
